{"tid":1820480,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台仔分享五大選舉之最","createTime":"2020-01-11T14:01:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-11T17:29:52.000Z","uid":254183,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"bd7dfb92f690dc798830b1078142cd51e9f0bcb6","tid":1820480,"uid":254183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T14:01:03.000Z","msg":"以下為個人心得<br />\n<br />\n1.最開心<br />\n感謝Korea Fish的胡言亂語胡說八道胡扯一通，成功逼出了八百萬不想讓你當選的選民，一舉刷波台灣總統得票之最<br />\n不過別擔心，總統選輸了，回到高雄還有罷免投票在等著你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.最難過<br />\n在眾多小黨的夾殺下，時力不分區只取得三席，國會戰神黃國昌確定落選<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n時力把黃國昌放在不分區第四席，就是想用他的名氣最大限度逼出選票，包括我個人在內<br />\n可惜還是功虧一潰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.最驚奇<br />\n雖然有著一堆奶共發言，但柯P還是靠著台北市長的執政能力，成功替民眾黨取得不分區席位四席，一舉超越時力成為第三大黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4.最欣慰<br />\n蔣萬安能在對上吳怡農的對決中獲勝，其實我是開心的<br />\n無論是同婚表決上，或是針對一國兩制率先發難，能明顯看出蔣萬安是站在年輕人這邊<br />\n我認為他是有能力改變國民黨生態的人物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n5.最無力<br />\n身為新北市民，在我的選區分區立委已經讓國民黨N連霸了，怎麼投就是投不贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過扣掉新北很藍這點，其實新北還是挺好的，離台北市區近交通方便但房價卻好平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0f0ee2b5b9c2f32ec521b1265d391aa76f1d470","tid":1820480,"uid":329842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T14:07:11.000Z","msg":"以樓主你的認知，台灣年青一輩(20-40歲)<br />\n藍綠比例是多少？"},{"pid":"e40c63e28fa5fdd11768d4b77b8abcc9ae455bbf","tid":1820480,"uid":12628,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T14:13:02.000Z","msg":"樓主，開玩笑一問，為何新北那麼多風化案？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85074227771f05091310230109f2fb92b463386f","tid":1820480,"uid":312333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd7dfb92f690dc798830b1078142cd51e9f0bcb6","tid":1820480,"uid":254183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T14:01:03.000Z","msg":"以下為個人心得<br />\n<br />\n1.最開心<br />\n感謝Korea Fish的胡言亂語胡說八道胡扯一通，成功逼出了八百萬不想讓你當選的選民，一舉刷波台灣總統得票之最<br />\n不過別擔心，總統選輸了，回到高雄還有罷免投票在等著你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.最難過<br />\n在眾多小黨的夾殺下，時力不分區只取得三席，國會戰神黃國昌確定落選<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n時力把黃國昌放在不分區第四席，就是想用他的名氣最大限度逼出選票，包括我個人在內<br />\n可惜還是功虧一潰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.最驚奇<br />\n雖然有著一堆奶共發言，但柯P還是靠著台北市長的執政能力，成功替民眾黨取得不分區席位四席，一舉超越時力成為第三大黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/do