f\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e4a42e2d3cdda8d7894eba83e4f47f3f0f2707d","tid":1820480,"uid":288670,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T14:22:49.000Z","msg":"3.最驚奇<br />\n雖然有著一堆奶共發言，但柯P還是靠著台北市長的執政能力，成功替民眾黨取得不分區席位四席，一舉超越時力成為第三大黨<br />\n<br />\n好撚擔心四年後弱智台仔會選左柯呢個暗共做總統 到時就仆街"},{"pid":"dd8fb7ddc1f85c90f5ea66e5427fadb31fed8f7a","tid":1820480,"uid":281401,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T14:24:46.000Z","msg":"蔣萬安係可造之材<br />\n2016逆境中勝出<br />\n2020絕境中穩住<br />\n<br />\n但佢必須將國民黨拉回正藍"},{"pid":"36dd2f7371988776632f1cb454ff13412fa43f97","tid":1820480,"uid":34410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T14:26:21.000Z","msg":"台灣基進黨點都好過左膠時代力量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a28187f0d26255500002305fdc3c11152ba1542","tid":1820480,"uid":34213,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T14:36:45.000Z","msg":"四年後係咪柯p同韓國瑜？<br />\n咁就大獲"},{"pid":"244a17351f9493fd28e5a94a10177941deae033a","tid":1820480,"uid":16846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T14:40:49.000Z","msg":"樓主點睇今次時代力量jer住民進黨唔放個選戰approach?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然港台都有啲政評鄙視佢哋咁打<br />\n但偏綠嘅細黨如果唔想俾民進黨食曬塊餅嘅話，似乎一定要咁做？<br />\n例如基進一路得到咁埋，臨尾催票都催唔返5%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3439a7a6f175c55437b08e527ee21f4916edd91","tid":1820480,"uid":281401,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3a28187f0d26255500002305fdc3c11152ba1542","tid":1820480,"uid":34213,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T14:36:45.000Z","msg":"四年後係咪柯p同韓國瑜？<br />\n咁就大獲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T14:42:22.000Z","msg":"韓國瑜冇架啦<br />\n連登實在太唔熟台灣<br />\n國民黨大把人會清算佢<br />\n佢好快會面臨罷免<br />\n<br />\n4年後柯p咩境況好難講，<br />\n民眾黨都係得4席。<br />\n佢不斷做錯決定都會收皮，<br />\n好似郭台銘咁，由形勢大好變收皮。"},{"pid":"894d6ba9eb52573c90e7d45b84ce32d7800d795a","tid":1820480,"uid":34213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"244a17351f9493fd28e5a94a10177941deae033a","tid":1820480,"uid":16846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T14:40:49.000Z","msg":"樓主點睇今次時代力量jer住民進黨唔放個選戰approach?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然港台都有啲政評鄙視佢哋咁打<br />\n但偏綠嘅細黨如果唔想俾民進黨食曬塊餅嘅話，似乎一定要咁做？<br />\n例如基進一路得到咁埋，臨尾催票都催唔返5%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T14:47:20.000Z","msg":"樓主好似係台仔？"},{"pid":"b9209fd3d6079b97949a8a434b5d22ff11bdee8a","tid":1820480,"uid":91721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T14:58:39.000Z","msg":"吳怡農不好嗎？"},{"pid":"6123d0ee59cd9ee0723cc4c0b558e0493d3fdf1e","tid":1820480,"uid":252069,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T15:03:51.000Z","msg":"屌你! 黃色經濟圈根本影響唔到d資源分配!<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不過無所謂<br />\n因為學波蘭人將抗爭融入生活先係目的</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">明明好成功,我哋錯咗重點啫,調整心態就得</span><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1820242\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1820242</a>"},{"pid":"ca5b25d5772a4367ceff5efa15112aac5aa586cf","tid":1820480,"uid":20170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9209fd3d6079b97949a8a434b5d22ff11bdee8a","tid":1820480,"uid":91721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T14:58:39.000Z","msg":"吳怡農不好嗎？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T15:09:04.000Z","msg":"唔係唔好<br />\n但身為執政黨，贏盡其實唔係好事<br />\n兩黨制之下，反對黨必須要有威脅性，先可以令執政黨有所警剔<br />\n但前題係，呢個反對黨唔會有危害國家嘅主張，例如接受中国統一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><b